OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith further outbreaks of light
OL,7,Fdrizzle, mainly over the high ground.
OL,8,FHowever, an organised band of rain
OL,9,Flikely to arrive from the northwest by
OL,10,Fthe evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FPatchy frost initially on Thursday,
OL,14,Fbut then fine with some sunshine.
OL,15,FTurning unsettled over the Easter
OL,16,Fweekend with showers or longer spells
OL,17,Fof rain. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,18,Ftoo.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
